| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3098 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6c11a2da-a2ba-591a-b6ee-e6235b58b0fa"
